Ɛyaa nabɛyɩ wɛna naalɛ nɛ pañɩɩna ɖama nɛ pala tʊmɩyɛ sɔsɔyɛ naɖɩyɛ. Payaɣ kacalaɣtʊ se Orville Wright nɛ palʊla-ɩ [[kɩyɛɛna fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 19 pɩnaɣ 1871 nɛ ɛsɩ [[kɔlaɣ fenaɣ]] 30 wiye pɩnaɣ 1948, ɛɛwɛna pɩnzɩ 76. Naalɛ tʊ yɔ  Wilbur Wright. Palʊla ɛlɛ kɛ [[ɖomaɣ fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 16 pɩnaɣ 1867 nɛ ɛsɩ [[agoza fenaɣ]] 30 wiye pɩnaɣ 1912 ɛɛwɛna pɩnsɩ 45. Panaalɛ mba kɛna [[Etaazuunii|Amerika]] taa [[ɛsɔdaa lɔɔɖɩyɛ|ɛsɔdaa lɔɔɖa]] lubu nɔsɩ yɔɔ mba. Pɛkɛ ñɩnɩyaa, tamasɩ lɩzɩya, lɩmaza lɩzɩya, tigila sɩya nɛ ɛsɔdaa lɔɔɖa saya. Ɛsɔdaa lɔɔɖa wena poluba yɔ avɛyɩ ɛzɩ wena awɛ nɛ panaɣ yɔ.

Lɔɔda ana ayɔɔ tosuli kʊɖʊ kʊɖʊ ɛlɛ a-yɔɔ wɛ haaa. Pɩnaɣ 1900 kɛ papaɣza ɛsɔdaa cɔʊ kpɛɛɛ kpɛɛɛ pɩkɔɔ pɩsɩɩna pɩnaɣ 1903, nɛ lɔɔɖa wena poluba yɔ, paɖʊ a-taa kɛ ciidu ñɩyʊ. Mba payaɣ-wɛ se Wright waa kɛ mbʊ yɔ, pɛkɛ Dayitɔ tɛtʊ taa ɛyaa, Ohiyo egeetiye taa, Etazunii  ɛjaɖɛ taa. Peeɖe patɔla [[cɛɛcɛ|cɛɛcɛɛnaa]] kiziŋjaku. Ɖalaa pɩnɛ pɛkɛna lɩmaɣza lɩzɩya nɛ pa-ñʊŋ taa nɛ lɛɛtʊ kamaɣ fɛyɩ mbʊ pʊ-yɔɔ, ɛsɔdaa lɔɔɖa luɖa, Otto Lilienthal yaa Octave Chanute, kɛ patɩɩzɩna nɛ pɩla poluba  ɛsɔdaa lɔɔɖɩyɛ nɖɩ pɛkɛdʊ ɖɩ-tɔm yɔ.

